preference.name: Step_export_data_format
preference.preference_description: Supports only the STEP AP214. These preferences have names of the relation types as their values. These values represent a relation type and are used to determine the Teamcenter and user-defined relation types from the relation-type part of the preference. Valid values are One or more strings; each string must be a valid relation type.
